 testing services nationally to reduce harm at music festivals and parties\r\nExpand treatment services for people suffering from drug problems\r\nEstablish more drug monitoring rooms to save lives and improve communities\r\nEnhance engagement services for disadvantaged young people\r\nEnd criminal charges that make getting help harder and ruin young lives for minor possession of illicit drugs\r\n\r\nWe need to give our kids a better chance. It’s not good enough to put our heads in the sand and tell them to “just say no”.\r\n\r\nWe need better tools and strategies to help our kids cope with the challenges of modern life.\r\n\r\nIt\'s time to end the fear tactics. It\'s time to end the marketing gimmicks. People need real resources to reduce the harms associated with drug use.\r\n\r\nAdd your name to take back control\r\n\r\nWe\'ll keep you updated about the campaign. Find out more here.'),(5157,520,'_petition_read_more','field_5deed566179da'),(5158,520,'petition_form_title',''),(5159,520,'_petition_form_title','field_5deed58b77e6b'),(5160,520,'petition_form',''),(5161,520,'_petition_form','field_5deed5a51f871'),(5162,521,'banner_head','Our drug laws are hurting our kids'),(5163,521,'_banner_head','field_5b568121a8ffe'),(5164,521,'banner_sub','We can get drugs under control by putting health and safety first.'),(5165,521,'_banner_sub','field_5b568139fd366'),(5166,521,'banner_button','<a href=\"btm btn-home\">Sign the petition</a>'),(5167,521,'_banner_button','field_5b568147fd367'),(5168,521,'page_col_image_2',''),(5169,521,'_page_col_image_2','field_5de6546e7c63a'),(5170,521,'sec_2_title',''),(5171,521,'_sec_2_title','field_5de6e3ef2798f'),(5172,521,'sec_2_text',''),(5173,521,'_sec_2_text','field_5de78dc89e613'),(5174,521,'sec_2_button',''),(5175,521,'_sec_2_button','field_5de6e58c86706'),(5176,521,'page_col_image_3',''),(5177,521,'_page_col_image_3','field_5de6e3998e07e'),(5178,521,'sec_3_title',''),(5179,521,'_sec_3_title','field_5de6e3d37d8da'),(5180,521,'sec_3_te