ges that make getting help harder and ruin young lives for minor possession of illicit drugs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe need to give our kids a better chance. It’s not good enough to put our heads in the sand and tell them to “just say no”.\r\n\r\nWe need better tools and strategies to help our kids cope with the challenges of modern life.\r\n\r\nIt\'s time to end the fear tactics. It\'s time to end the marketing gimmicks. People need real resources to reduce the harms associated with drug use.\r\n\r\nAdd your name to take back control\r\n\r\nWe\'ll keep you updated about the campaign. Find out more here.\r\n\r\n[/expand]'),(9587,771,'_petition_read_more','field_5deed566179da'),(9588,771,'_petition_read_more','field_5deed566179da'),(9589,771,'petition_form_title','Add your name to take back control'),(9590,771,'petition_form_title','Add your name to take back control'),(9591,771,'_petition_form_title','field_5deed58b77e6b'),(9592,771,'_petition_form_title','field_5deed58b77e6b'),(9593,771,'petition_form','[gravityform id=\"5\" title=\"false\" description=\"false\" ajax=\"true\"]'),(9594,771,'petition_form','[gravityform id=\"5\" title=\"false\" description=\"false\" ajax=\"true\"]'),(9595,771,'_petition_form','field_5deed5a51f871'),(9596,771,'_petition_form','field_5deed5a51f871'),(9597,771,'plan_icons_row_0_plan_icon_text','Roll out pill testing services nationally to reduce harm at music festivals and parties'),(9598,771,'plan_icons_row_0_plan_icon_text','Roll out pill testing services nationally to reduce harm at music festivals and parties'),(9599,771,'_plan_icons_row_0_plan_icon_text','field_5deed4ca61e91'),(9600,771,'_plan_icons_row_0_plan_icon_text','field_5deed4ca61e91'),(9601,771,'plan_icons_row_1_plan_icon_text','Expand treatment services for people suffering from drug problems'),(9602,771,'plan_icons_row_1_plan_icon_text','Expand treatment services for people suffering from drug problems'),(9603,771,'_plan_icons_row_1_plan_icon_text','field_5deed4ca61e91'),(9604