key-points\">\r\n 	<li><i class=\"fas fa-times\"></i> Young people can get drugs easily and don’t know what they’re taking.</li>\r\n 	<li><i class=\"fas fa-times\"></i> Lives are being ruined with severe criminal charges for minor possession.</li>\r\n 	<li><i class=\"fas fa-times\"></i> Despite dealers being caught every day, more simply replace them.</li>\r\n 	<li><i class=\"fas fa-times\"></i> It’s hard for people with problems to get help because they’re treated like criminals.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(14036,889,'_intro_bullets','field_5dee2fc3210e1'),(14037,889,'intro_text','This is because our governments leave drugs to an uncontrollable black market.'),(14038,889,'_intro_text','field_5dee2fd3e66b2'),(14039,889,'plan_title','Here\'s our common sense plan for <b> safer, saner drug laws </b> that put health and safety first:'),(14040,889,'_plan_title','field_5deed4957e419'),(14041,889,'plan_icons_row_0_plan_icon','516'),(14042,889,'_plan_icons_row_0_plan_icon','field_5deed4bc61e90'),(14043,889,'plan_icons_row_0_',''),(14044,889,'_plan_icons_row_0_','field_5deed4ca61e91'),(14045,889,'plan_icons_row_1_plan_icon','515'),(14046,889,'_plan_icons_row_1_plan_icon','field_5deed4bc61e90'),(14047,889,'plan_icons_row_1_',''),(14048,889,'_plan_icons_row_1_','field_5deed4ca61e91'),(14049,889,'plan_icons_row_2_plan_icon','514'),(14050,889,'_plan_icons_row_2_plan_icon','field_5deed4bc61e90'),(14051,889,'plan_icons_row_2_',''),(14052,889,'_plan_icons_row_2_','field_5deed4ca61e91'),(14053,889,'plan_icons_row_3_plan_icon','513'),(14054,889,'_plan_icons_row_3_plan_icon','field_5deed4bc61e90'),(14055,889,'plan_icons_row_3_',''),(14056,889,'_plan_icons_row_3_','field_5deed4ca61e91'),(14057,889,'plan_icons_row_4_plan_icon','512'),(14058,889,'_plan_icons_row_4_plan_icon','field_5deed4bc61e90'),(14059,889,'plan_icons_row_4_',''),(14060,889,'_plan_icons_row_4_','field_5deed4ca61e91'),(14061,889,'plan_icons_row','5'),(14062,889,'_plan_icons_row','field_5deed4aa61e8f'),(14063,889,'petition_intro_h