ls and strategies to help their kids cope with the challenges of modern life.\r\n\r\nIt’s not good enough to put our heads in the sand and tell our kids to “just say no”. It doesn\'t work.\r\n\r\nIt\'s time to end the fear tactics. It\'s time to end the marketing gimmicks. People need real resources to reduce the harms associated with drug use.\r\n\r\nOur state and federal governments need to work together to get drug use under control by putting health and safety first.'),(15373,907,'_intro_bullets','field_5df5c6799d05a'),(15374,907,'intro_text',''),(15375,907,'_intro_text','field_5df5c6799d0c6'),(15376,907,'plan_title',''),(15377,907,'_plan_title','field_5df5c6799d197'),(15378,907,'plan_icons_row','5'),(15379,907,'_plan_icons_row','field_5df5c6799d211'),(15380,907,'plan_icons_row_0_plan_icon','516'),(15381,907,'_plan_icons_row_0_plan_icon','field_5df5c679a8044'),(15382,907,'plan_icons_row_0_plan_icon_text',' Roll out pill testing services nationally to reduce harm at music festivals and parties'),(15383,907,'_plan_icons_row_0_plan_icon_text','field_5df5c679a80ae'),(15384,907,'plan_icons_row_1_plan_icon','515'),(15385,907,'_plan_icons_row_1_plan_icon','field_5df5c679a8044'),(15386,907,'plan_icons_row_1_plan_icon_text','Expand treatment services for people suffering from drug problems'),(15387,907,'_plan_icons_row_1_plan_icon_text','field_5df5c679a80ae'),(15388,907,'plan_icons_row_2_plan_icon','514'),(15389,907,'_plan_icons_row_2_plan_icon','field_5df5c679a8044'),(15390,907,'plan_icons_row_2_plan_icon_text','Establish more drug monitoring rooms to save lives and improve communities'),(15391,907,'_plan_icons_row_2_plan_icon_text','field_5df5c679a80ae'),(15392,907,'plan_icons_row_3_plan_icon','513'),(15393,907,'_plan_icons_row_3_plan_icon','field_5df5c679a8044'),(15394,907,'plan_icons_row_3_plan_icon_text','Enhance engagement services for disadvantaged young people'),(15395,907,'_plan_icons_row_3_plan_icon_text','field_5df5c679a80ae'),(15396,907,'plan_icons_row_4_plan